    "Alfred Akirov is the founder and Chairman of Alrov Group, an Israeli real estate and hospitality company based in Tel Aviv.",
    "Born in Iraq in January 1941, he immigrated to Israel with his family in 1952.",
    "He began his career in construction at his father's business before venturing into textiles and fashion, and then shifting into real estate and investments.",
    "He founded Alrov Group in 1978 and has since expanded the company into real estate, luxury hotels, and financial holdings both in Israel and abroad."
